description: PDX Dönerländ is shaking up Portland's street food scene in ways you've never seen! Turkish and German street food is a fantastic way to shake up your every day routine. Made from organic and locally sourced ingredients, every bite from this food truck is guaranteed fresh and delicious! The best flatbread sandwiches you'll ever see are right around the corner today, at PDX Dönerländ!
name: PDX Dönerländ
